comment: * A {@link Parcelable} value type that contains information about an account authenticator.

variables.name: type
variables.comment: The string that uniquely identifies an authenticator

variables.name: labelId
variables.comment: A resource id of a label for the authenticator that is suitable for displaying

variables.name: iconId
variables.comment: A resource id of a icon for the authenticator

variables.name: smallIconId
variables.comment: A resource id of a smaller icon for the authenticator

variables.name: accountPreferencesId
variables.comment:
* A resource id for a hierarchy of PreferenceScreen to be added to the settings page for the
     * account. See {@link AbstractAccountAuthenticator} for an example.

variables.name: packageName
variables.comment: The package name that can be used to lookup the resources from above.

variables.name: customTokens
variables.comment: Authenticator handles its own token caching and permission screen

variables.name: CREATOR
variables.comment: Used to create the object from a parcel.
